## Contributing

When adding new patterns:

1. Follow the established directory structure
2. Use the MDC format for documentation
3. Include practical examples
4. Link to related patterns
5. Update relevant index files

## Version Control

These patterns are versioned with the project. See [Commit Conventions](mdc:deployment/commit-conventions.mdc) for contribution guidelines.
